<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>922</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 shén de ér nǚ ya bù yào hài pà, mò hòu de zāi nán yǒu duō dà.
 zhǐ yào nǐ jiān xìn yī kào jìng wèi yé hé huá. tā bì bǎo hù wǒ men de jiā.
 xiàn zài shì mò shì le, zhǔ yé sū yào huí lái le.
 shì shàng fā shēng de shì dōu yīng yàn le zhǔ de huà. kuài jǐng xǐng chuán fú yīn ba.</lyrics>
<title>shén de ér nǚ ya bù yào hài pà 迦南922</title>
</song>